ing?","Bekijk onze vacatures","/word-onze-collega/vacatures",{"id":103,"name":104,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":105,"height":106,"formats":18,"hash":107,"ext":108,"mime":109,"size":110,"url":111,"previewUrl":18,"provider":53,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":112,"updatedAt":113,"documentId":114,"publishedAt":56,"focalPoint":18},{"id":191,"name":192,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":106,"height":106,"formats":18,"hash":193,"ext":108,"mime":109,"size":194,"url":195,"previewUrl":18,"provider":53,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":196,"updatedAt":197,"documentId":198,"publishedAt":56,"focalPoint":18},8,"briefcase.svg","briefcase_679abae475",4.49,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/briefcase_679abae475.svg","2023-08-17T08:31:37.038Z","2025-01-24T15:53:51.531Z","bfdftlvwhj35dm37dzv4aujf",[200,243,282,316,350],{"id":201,"title":202,"subTitle":18,"content":203,"callToActionText":204,"callToActionLink":185,"colorStyle":205,"showAsides":91,"imageUrl":206,"__component":242},16,"Power Platform governance: de balans tussen beveiliging en innovatie","Het is belangrijk om een balans te vinden tussen beveiliging en innovatie binnen jouw organisatie. Hoewel governance noodzakelijk is, moeten je medewerkers en teams de ruimte krijgen om waarde te creëren voor zowel henzelf als de onderneming.\n\nOnze Power Platform-specialisten staan klaar om je te adviseren over de diverse mogelijkheden. We begeleiden je tijdens het ontwikkelen en implementeren van een effectieve governance- en omgevingsstrategie, zodat je het beste uit het Microsoft Power Platform kunt halen.","Wil je meer weten? Neem contact met ons op.","Sugar Glaze",{"id":207,"name":208,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":209,"height":210,"formats":211,"hash":237,"ext":146,"mime":149,"size":238,"url":239,"previewUrl":18,"provider":53,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":240,"updatedAt":240,"documentId":241,"publishedAt":56,"focalPoint":18},793,"Power Platform update.png",2234,2000,{"l