Onze ervaren developers ontwikkelen de toepassing volledig voor je.","White",{"id":249,"name":250,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":251,"height":252,"formats":253,"hash":277,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":278,"url":279,"previewUrl":18,"provider":53,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":280,"updatedAt":280,"documentId":281,"publishedAt":56,"focalPoint":18},764,"maatwerk.jpg",1280,850,{"large":254,"small":260,"medium":266,"thumbnail":272},{"ext":23,"url":255,"hash":256,"mime":26,"name":257,"path":18,"size":258,"width":29,"height":259},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e.jpg","large_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e","large_maatwerk.jpg",64.15,664,{"ext":23,"url":261,"hash":262,"mime":26,"name":263,"path":18,"size":264,"width":16,"height":265},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e.jpg","small_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e","small_maatwerk.jpg",19.69,332,{"ext":23,"url":267,"hash":268,"mime":26,"name":269,"path":18,"size":270,"width":41,"height":271},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e.jpg","medium_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e","medium_maatwerk.jpg",39.51,498,{"ext":23,"url":273,"hash":274,"mime":26,"name":275,"path":18,"size":276,"width":182,"height":236},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e.jpg","thumbnail_maatwerk_b13f4ae62e","thumbnail_maatwerk.jpg",5.55,"maatwerk_b13f4ae62e",96.54,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/maatwerk_b13f4ae62e.jpg","2024-08-01T11:43:49.966Z","z85xixi08lol9621vn40pi13",{"id":283,"title":284,"subTitle":18,"content":285,"callToActionText":18,"callToActionLink":18,"colorStyle":205,"showAsides":91,"imageUrl":286,"__component":242},18,"Power Platform staat aan, wat nu?","Het Power Platform wordt al gebruikt in jouw organisatie. Een aantal enthousiaste collega's hebben al mooie apps gemaakt en je staat op het punt om het Power Platform in te zetten voor bedrijfskritische processen. Maar je weet niet precies hoe je dit het beste kunt aanpakken.\n\nWij begeleiden je in dit proces en samen bepalen we de \"next steps\". Onze architecten voeren een volledige omgevings- en securitycheck uit, wat resulteert in een omgevingsstrategie, governance, en een ontwikkel- en adoptieplan.",{"id":287,"name":288,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":251,"height":252,"formats":289,"hash":310,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":311,"url":312,"previewUrl":18,"provider":53,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":313,"updatedAt":314,"documentId":315,"publishedAt":56,"focalPoint":18},765,"power platform.jpg",{"large":290,"small":295,"medium":300,"thumbnail":305},{"ext":23,"url":291,"hash":292,"mime":26,"name":293,"path":18,"size":294,"width":29,"height":259},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_power_platform_39c53ca01e.jpg","large_power_platform_39c53ca01e","large_power platform.jpg",208.02,{"ext":23,"url":296,"hash":297,"mime":26,"name":298,"path":18,"size":299,"width":16,"height":265},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_power_platform_39c53ca01e.jpg","small_power_platform_39c53ca01e","small_power platform.jpg",66.01,{"ext":23,"url":301,"hash":302,"mime":26,"name":303,"path":18,"size":304,"width":41,"height":271},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_power_platform_39c53ca01e.jpg","medium_power_platform_39c53ca01e","medium_power platform.jpg",131.84,{"ext":23,"url":306,"hash":307,"mime":26,"name":308,"path":18,"size":309,"width":182,"height":236},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_power_platform_39c53ca01e.jpg","thumbnail_power_platform_39c53ca01e","thumbnail_power platform.jpg",17.35,"power_platform_39c53ca01e",304.58,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/power_platform_39c53ca01e.jpg","2024-08-01T11:43:50.458Z","2024-08-01T11:43:59.138Z","gic37kkycc1gz3zx65l4himw",{"id":317,"title":318,"subTitle":18,"content":319,"callToActionText":320,"callToAct